      <span class="headers">'Shopping Guide' for PoTC Quests</span>
<p>
<p>
There are many, many items that need to be collected if you are making these items yourself (or if you are providing supplies in order to have someone else make the items for you). Gladlyn, with the aid of the EQTC message board community, has kindly put together a "shopping list" for the items needed for this involved quest.
</p>
<h3>Master list of items needed (assuming NO failures)</h3>
<ul> 
<li>1 Allspice</li> 
<li>1 Barley</li> 
<li>1 Benzoin</li> 
<li>2 Bottle</li> 
<li>1 Branch of Planar Oak</li> 
<li>1 Brownie Parts</li> 
<li>1 Cake Round</li> 
<li>21 Celestial Solvent (for Celestial Essence)</li> 
<li>1 Cream</li> 
<li>1 Curved Blade Mold</li> 
<li>1 Dragon Egg</li> 
<li>2 Eggs (for 2 clumps of dough)</li> 
<li>3 Elven Wine</li> 
<li>9 Emerald - 7 Imbued Emerald (Dust)</li> 
<li>1 Enchanted Bar of Silver</li> 
<li>2 enchanted block of clay</li> 
<li>1 Eucalyptus</li> 
<li>1 Fennel</li> 
<li>1 File</li> 
<li>3 Flour (2 for 2 clumps of dough)</li> 
<li>7 Frosting</li> 
<li>1 Fruit</li> 
<li>2 Gold Bar (1 Enchanted Gold Bar )</li> 
<li>2 Grapes</li> 
<li>2 High Quality Firing Sheet</li> 
<li>1 Hilt Mold</li> 
<li>1 Hops</li> 
<li>1 Idol Sketch</li> 
<li>1 Imbued Plains Pebble</li> 
<li>2 Imbued Plains Pebble (Dust)</li> 
<li>1 Iron Oxide</li> 
<li>8 Jar of Acid</li> 
<li>1 Jar of Lacquer</li> 
<li>3 Jumjum Stalk</li> 
<li>1 Lead Sulfide</li> 
<li>1 Lettuce</li> 
<li>1 Limestone</li> 
<li>1 Loaf of Bread</li> 
<li>2 Mandrake Roots</li> 
<li>8 Metal Bits</li> 
<li>8 Milk (2 for 2 clumps of dough)</li> 
<li>3 Mistletoe</li> 
<li>1 Needle Mold</li> 
<li>1 Opal</li> 
<li>1 Permafrost Crystals</li> 
<li>1 Pie Tin</li> 
<li>1 Pommel Mold</li> 
<li>1 Rennet</li> 
<li>21 Research (for Celestial Essence)</li> 
<li>2 Rubes</li> 
<li>1 Sandalwood</li> 
<li>4 Sapphires (2 for Distilled mana)</li> 
<li>1 Scaler Mold</li> 
<li>1 Sculpting Tools</li> 
<li>3 Sheet of Metal</li> 
<li>1 Small Brick of Ore</li> 
<li>1 Smithy Hammer</li> 
<li>1 Soda</li> 
<li>1 Spices</li> 
<li>6 Spider Silks</li> 
<li>6 Spiderlings Silks (Silk Cord = 3 Silk Threads )</li> 
<li>1 Star Ruby</li> 
<li>1 Steel Boning</li> 
<li>1 Sweet Lotus Sap (sticky lotus sap *or*petals)</li> 
<li>1 tackle box</li> 
<li>1 Tunic Pattern</li> 
<li>1 Vegetables</li> 
<li>2 Velium Bits (4 small pieces of velium and 2 coldain tempers)</li> 
<li>1 Vial of Distilled Mana (poison vial 2 sapphires)</li> 
<li>10 water</li> 
<li>1 Wild Cabbage</li> 
<li>1 Wine Yeast</li>
</ul> <h3>Breakdown by Tradeskill </h3> <i>(click on the skill name to access the trade supply listing for those supplies) </i>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Baking&menustr=110030000000">Baking:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>1 Spices</li> 
<li>8 Milk (2 for 2 clumps of dough, 1 for cream)</li> 
<li>1 Loaf of Bread</li> 
<li>1 Lettuce</li> 
<li>3 Jumjum Stalk</li> 
<li>3 Flour (2 for 2 clumps of dough)</li> 
<li>7 Frosting</li> 
<li>2 Eggs (for 2 clumps of dough)</li> 
<li>1 Cream</li> 
<li>10 water flasks</li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Brewing&menustr=110040000000">Brewing:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>1 Wine Yeast</li> 
<li>1 Soda</li> 
<li>2 Grapes</li> 
<li>1 Hops</li> 
<li>2 Bottles</li> 
<li>1 Barley</li> 
<li>3 Elven Wine</li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Pottery&menustr=110100000000">Pottery:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>2 blocks of magic clay<i> (large block of clay upon which an enchanter has cast "enchant clay")</i></li> 
<li>2 High Quality Firing Sheet</li> 
<li>1 Sculpting Tools</li> 
<li>1 Idol Sketch</li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Alchemy&menustr=110020000000">Alchemy:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>1 Allspice</li> 
<li>1 Benzoin</li> 
<li>1 Eucalyptus</li> 
<li>1 Fennel</li> 
<li>2 Mandrake Roots</li> 
<li>3 Mistletoe</li> 
<li>1 Sandalwood</li> 
<li>1 Rennet</li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Smithing&menustr=110110000000">Smithing:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>21 Celestial Solvent (for Celestial Essence)</li> 
<li>8 Jar of Acid</li> 
<li>3 Sheet of Metal</li> 
<li>1 Small Brick of Ore</li> 
<li>1 Scaler Mold</li> 
<li>1 Pommel Mold</li> 
<li>1 Needle Mold</li> 
<li>8 Metal Bits (2 for boning)</li> 
<li>1 Hilt Mold</li> 
<li>1 Curved Blade Mold</li> 
<li>1 File</li> 
<li>1 Smithy Hammer</li> 
<li>1 Steel Boning</li> 
<li>2 Velium Bits (4 small pieces of velium and 2 coldain temper) </li> 
<li>4 small pieces of velium</li> 
<li>2 coldain velium tempers </li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Tailoring&menustr=110130000000">Tailoring:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>6 Spider Silks</li> 
<li>6 Spiderlings Silks (Silk Cord = 3 Silk Threads )</li> 
<li>1 Tunic Pattern</li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Jewelcraft&menustr=110080000000">Jewelcraft:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>9 Emerald - 7 Imbued Emerald (Dust)</li> 
<li>1 Enchanted Bar of Silver</li> 
<li>2 Gold Bar (1 Enchanted Gold Bar )</li> 
<li>2 Rubies</li> 
<li>1 Star Ruby</li> 
<li>4 Sapphires (2 for Distilled mana)</li> 
<li>1 Opal</li> 
<li>1 Vial of Distilled Mana (<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1388">poison vial</a>, 2 sapphires)</li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_zbt_page.php?st=Foraged&menustr=110070000000">Forage:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>1 Fruit</li> 
<li>1 Dragon Egg</li> 
<li>1 Branch of Planar Oak</li> 
<li>1 Vegetables</li> 
<li>1 Wild Cabbage</li> 
<li>1 Imbued Plains Pebble</li> 
<li>2 Imbued Plains Pebble (Dust)</li>
</ul>
<p>
Drops/found:
</p>
<ul> 
<li>1 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1539">Iron Oxide</a></li> 
<li>1 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1384">Permafrost Crystals</a></li> 
<li>21 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1190">Celestial Essence</a> Recipes</li> 
<li>1 Sweet Lotus Sap (<i>or</i> sticky lotus sap <i>or</i> soft lotus petals <i>or</i> black lotus stem)</li>
</ul>
<p>
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Make%20Poison&menustr=110090000000">Poison:</a>
</p>
<ul> 
<li>1 Limestone</li> 
<li>1 Iron Oxide</li> 
<li>1 Lead Sulfide</li>
</ul>
<p>
Containers and misc.:
</p>
<ul> 
<li>1 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1745">Mortar and pestal</a></li> 
<li>1 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1192">tackle box</a></li> 
<li>1 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1122">Dairy Spoon</a> is player made</li> 
<li>1 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1761">Cake Round</a> is player made</li>
<li>1 <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1217">Pie Tin</a> is player made</li>
</ul>
